{"tid":489564,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"多謝巴打支持 from 廣東話講解 C/C++ on YouTube","createTime":"2017-12-04T20:17:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-24T16:47:14.000Z","uid":131100,"like":255,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"31b77ae439b54ae8e3b2cddc710188f8e93a75d2","tid":489564,"uid":131100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T20:17:13.000Z","msg":"(之前個 post 沉左底 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/335336/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/335336/page/1</a>  )<br />\n<br />\n今日 upload 左第 100 條片, 亦剛剛完成一個系列<br />\n整個 C++ Tutorial Project 我花左總共 5 個用既時間, 終於可以講晒當初訂下既 Topics<br />\n <br />\nBasic C<br />\nAdvance C<br />\nC to C++<br />\nAdvance C++<br />\nUI in Win32 API<br />\nDatabase<br />\nUnix Programming in C++<br />\nNetwork Socket<br />\nUnicode<br />\nRay Tracing 3D Rendering<br />\nOpenGL<br />\nAdvance OpenGL<br />\nUnreal C++<br />\nShading Language<br />\n<br />\n雖然都只係皮毛, 但希望可以幫到初學既人, 解釋基本概念, 同俾到個學習方向<br />\nD 片睇既人都已經俾我預期既多, 本身知道 C++ 並唔係咩大路野, 未必有太多人會想學<br />\n而且廣東話既片真係好難 promote, 所以可以既話希望大家幫手 Share 出去<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCWW9g_90Ik1U8ULNG5PvoYQ/featured\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCWW9g_90Ik1U8ULNG5PvoYQ%2Ffeatured&d=ENFd%2Flb2Gs3BEX6GkT3qcDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=377bc109\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCWW9g_90Ik1U8ULNG5PvoYQ/featured</a><br />\n<br />\n最後好多謝連登巴打既支持, 拍到一半既時候的確有覺得攰, 不過見到巴打既留言, 令我有動力完成埋佢<br />\n<br />\n依個 2017 既 Project 就已經完成, 之後未必會好似之前咁密去 upload 片<br />\n不過有 C++ 既問題, 係歡迎係 youtube 留言 or facebook inbox 問, 我會盡力去答<br />\n<br />\n2017 亦到左年尾, 係度同大家講聲 Merry X'mas &amp; Happy New Year 2018"},{"pid":"303ef8db2713d9ffc0b8ba67828d88d5ef8f26b8","tid":489564,"uid":131100,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T20:19:52.000Z","msg":"5 個用既時間<br />\n5 個*月*既時間"},{"pid":"71ead5c51dcaac29ee41fcc0ecfaba2802afa95e","tid":489564,"uid":84507,"