ore":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T15:04:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想問下風教授, 你個video course有冇提及C++ style guide? 你有冇乜嘢good advice? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(P.S. Google嗰個好似太strict, 好多人反對用! GNU (coding standard)嗰個又好似太闊鬆噉, 乜都得!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )</blockquote><br />\ncpp core guide line？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nAny reference? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n叔叔係咪講緊呢個: <a href=\"https://github.com/isocpp/CppCoreGuidelines/blob/master/CppCoreGuidelines.md#S-introduction\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fisocpp%2FCppCoreGuidelines%2Fblob%2Fmaster%2FCppCoreGuidelines.md%23S-introduction&d=ENFd%2Flb2Gs3BEX6GkT3qcDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=c0aac420\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/isocpp/CppCoreGuidelines/blob/master/CppCoreGuidelines.md#S-introduction</a> ?<br />\n係嘅話就唔係我想要嘅嘢, 我係要naming conventions, indentation style, whether to separate public(header files) from private(main.cpp) interface呢啲..."},{"pid":"98320ac0dead83db3c3b4f0dc01918bb586cbda3","tid":489564,"uid":113776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T15:13:23.000Z","msg":"留名支持"},{"pid":"90418d19e608ae7014bdfcb543e8b9277d9c78ad","tid":489564,"uid":131100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T15:22:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想問下風教授, 你個video course有冇提及C++ style guide? 你有冇乜嘢good advice? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(P.S. Google嗰個好似太strict, 好多人反對用! GNU (coding standard)嗰個又好似太闊鬆噉, 乜都得!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )</blockquote><br />\ncpp core guide line？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nAny reference? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n叔叔係咪講緊呢個: <a href=\"https://github.com/isocpp/CppCoreGuidelines/blob/master/CppCoreGuidelines.md#S-introduction\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fisocpp%2FCppCoreGuidelines%2Fblob%2Fmaster%2FCppCoreGuidelines.md%23S-introduction&d=ENFd%2Flb2Gs3BEX6GkT3qcDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=c0aac420\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/isocpp/CppCoreGuidelines/blob/master/CppCoreGuidelines.md#S-introduction</a> ?<br />\n係嘅話就唔係我想要嘅嘢, 我係要naming conventions, indentation style, whether to separate public(header files) from private(main.cpp) interface呢啲...</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我個人就無一個 Style guide, 都係是但搵個黎跟<br />\n之於工作上就跟返公司用咩, 其實個個都差唔到好多,<br />\n跟過幾個之後都知大路係要D咩, <br />\n好多時D人執著都只係 tab / space 或者 { 係唔係同一行<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可以睇返我之前整左個 Open Source 既 Cross-platform library<br />\n<a href=\"https://github.com/Jasonchan35/libax\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2FJasonchan35%2Flibax&d=ENFd%2Flb2Gs3BEX6GkT3qcDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=a539fec2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/Jasonchan35/libax</a><br />\n<br />\n不過都好幾年無 update, <br />\n整左新個 version 改左 design 用 C++11 同 exception<br />\n有時間再 Open Source 左佢"},{"pid":"a4e94dc70ce9b444dbdd79856523a41215d07b4e","tid":489564,"uid":131100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T15:26:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會講下cmake<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都可以既, 不過應該唔算太難, 如果明白 Makefile 係做咩<br />\n有無 D 有問題既實際例子, 咁我睇下用黎做示範<br />\n<br />\n另外因為我唔太喜歡 cmake, 所以自己整左個 Project Generator 出 VC, xcode, makefile<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://github.com/Jasonchan35/ax_project_gen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2FJasonchan35%2Fax_project_gen&d=ENFd%2Flb2Gs3BEX6GkT3qcDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=4cbaa15b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/Jasonchan35/ax_project_gen</a>"},{"pid":"2848f9166c72727036889a9bb083bf2d9fbfead6","tid":489564,"uid":59052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T15:30:54.000Z","msg":"會唔會講下python同c#"},{"pid":"4095c443eda1a471c6a407ccd281f1de9d0525da","tid":489564,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T16:04:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想問下風教授, 你個video course有冇提及C++ style guide? 你有冇乜嘢good advice? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(P.S. Google嗰個好似太strict, 好多人反對用! GNU (coding standard)嗰個又好似太闊鬆噉, 乜都得!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )</blockquote><br />\ncpp core guide line？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nAny reference? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n叔叔係咪講緊呢個: <a href=\"https://github.com/isocpp/CppCoreGuidelines/blob/master/CppCoreGuidelines.md#S-introduction\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fisocpp%2FCppCoreGuidelines%2Fblob%2Fmaster%2FCppCoreGuidelines.md%23S-introduction&d=ENFd%2Flb2Gs3BEX6GkT3qcDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=c0aac420\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/isocpp/CppCoreGuidelines/blob/master/CppCoreGuidelines.md#S-introduction</a> ?<br />\n係嘅話就唔係我想要嘅嘢, 我係要naming conventions, indentation style, whether to separate public(header files) from private(main.cpp) interface呢啲...</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我個人就無一個 Style guide, 都係是但搵個黎跟<br />\n之於工作上就跟返公司用咩, 其實個個都差唔到好多,<br />\n跟過幾個之後都知大路係要D咩, <br />\n好多時D人執著都只係 tab / space 或者 { 係唔係同一行<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可以睇返我之前整左個 Open Source 既 Cross-platform library<br />\n<a href=\"https://github.com/Jasonchan35/libax\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2FJasonchan35%2Flibax&d=ENFd%2Flb2Gs3BEX6GkT3qcDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=a539fec2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/Jasonchan35/libax</a><br />\n<br />\n不過都好幾年無 update, <br />\n整左新個 version 改左 design 用 C++11 同 exception<br />\n有時間再 Open Source 左佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\noic, thanks!<br />\n<br />\nBTW, C啲coding style好standard下, 個個都差不多; 但C++真係五花八門, 各有各做噉! 依你所見, 即係&quot;No style is the best style!&quot;啦, 明白晒! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"345ce3995d0f8dd4ff23ce549d80e002ebd39a6a","tid":489564,"uid":131100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T16:36:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想問下風教授, 你個video course有冇提及C++ style guide? 你有冇乜嘢good advice? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(P.S. Google嗰個好似太strict, 好多人反對用! GNU (coding standard)嗰個又好似太闊鬆噉, 乜都得!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )</blockquote><br />\ncpp core guide line？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nAny reference? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n叔叔係咪講緊呢個: <a href=\"https://github.com/isocpp/CppCoreGuidelines/blob/master/CppCoreGuidelines.md#S-introduction\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fisocpp%2FCppCoreGuidelines%2Fblob%2Fmaster%2FCppCoreGuidelines.md%23S-introduction&d=ENFd%2Flb2Gs3BEX6GkT3qcDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=c0aac420\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/isocpp/CppCoreGuidelines/blob/master/CppCoreGuidelines.md#S-introduction</a> ?<br />\n係嘅話就唔係我想要嘅嘢, 我係要naming conventions, indentation style, whether to separate public(header files) from private(main.cpp) interface呢啲...</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我個人就無一個 Style guide, 都係是但搵個黎跟<br />\n之於工作上就跟返公司用咩, 其實個個都差唔到好多,<br />\n跟過幾個之後都知大路係要D咩, <br />\n好多時D人執著都只係 tab / space 或者 { 係唔係同一行<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可以睇返我之前整左個 Open Source 既 Cross-platform library<br />\n<a href=\"https://github.com/Jasonchan35/libax\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2FJasonchan35%2Flibax&d=ENFd%2Flb2Gs3BEX6GkT3qcDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=a539fec2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/Jasonchan35/libax</a><br />\n<br />\n不過都好幾年無 update, <br />\n整左新個 version 改左 design 用 C++11 同 exception<br />\n有時間再 Open Source 左佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\noic, thanks!<br />\n<br />\nBTW, C啲coding style好standard下, 個個都差不多; 但C++真係五花八門, 各有各做噉! 依你所見, 即係&quot;No style is the best style!&quot;啦, 明白晒! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同一個 Project 當然最好用同一個 Style, 只係唔會有所謂最好既 Style,<br />\n所以我會是但搵一個黎跟就好, 反正結果都係一樣, 而且到最後都會有一D唔一致既地方, 例如個 Project 係用 Camel case (myTestingFunc), 但係又會用 STL (vector.push_back), 結果都係唔一致, 所以唔好太執著"},{"pid":"71723a81a657e8ba3937df33e3d0183229ed84d9","tid":489564,"uid":131100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T16:43:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會講下python同c#</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果多人想要既話可以考慮下既, <br />\n<br />\n原本諗著唔係咁多人係學 Python / C# 入門時有大問題, 所以無諗著講<br />\n<br />\n反而 Python 做 Maya Plugin 就真係冷門 D, 可能唔知邊度學, 可以講下<br />\n<br />\nC# 既情況都係一樣, Advance Topic 既可以講 <br />\n- C++ 同 C# 之間點溝通<br />\n- C# GC 原理"},{"pid":"704365016a08b96fd35f2e41df3adfa81bedcb85","tid":489564,"uid":114178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T00:20:29.000Z","msg":"即使係exp engineer對住C++都會需要struggle，感激巴打貢獻<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94156c5743d894a693fc807ee899f56e047c7b27","tid":489564,"uid":5056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T01:11:30.000Z","msg":"勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a04e6c81311fd7a05c0f84f360156ec266ac655a","tid":489564,"uid":78011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T01:22:41.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n評已正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed0363c2d852e7c59d16727cbc682e0239d841b8","tid":489564,"uid":48679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T01:38:28.000Z","msg":"雖然唔洗學，不過都俾個good 你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明知有汗出，無糧出都咁用心真係難得"},{"pid":"ff83e23f7e74542b405380db228e43ad0ba91098","tid":489564,"uid":30592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T01:40:07.000Z","msg":"留名學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3c35ba7c64e7af121d0a461f44704b504bab0e7","tid":489564,"uid":48679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T01:40:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會講下python同c#</blockquote><br />\n你睇完c++系列自己就會識呢兩個架啦"},{"pid":"7e7f8fd26e3abb2cbca44065101b00d14b5f409d","tid":489564,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T01:46:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>會唔會講下cmake<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都可以既, 不過應該唔算太難, 如果明白 Makefile 係做咩<br />\n有無 D 有問題既實際例子, 咁我睇下用黎做示範<br />\n<br />\n另外因為我唔太喜歡 cmake, 所以自己整左個 Project Generator 出 VC, xcode, makefile<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://github.com/Jasonchan35/ax_project_gen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2FJasonchan35%2Fax_project_gen&d=ENFd%2Flb2Gs3BEX6GkT3qcDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=4cbaa15b\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/Jasonchan35/ax_project_gen</a></blockquote><br />\n你自己用就ok,但要release出去cmake應該無得避"},{"pid":"c337af1a22300f3997646adc1904d90ea8ef2c06","tid":489564,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T01:48:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>會唔會講下cmake<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm