"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T02:18:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>會唔會講下python同c#</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果多人想要既話可以考慮下既, <br />\n<br />\n原本諗著唔係咁多人係學 Python / C# 入門時有大問題, 所以無諗著講<br />\n<br />\n反而 Python 做 Maya Plugin 就真係冷門 D, 可能唔知邊度學, 可以講下<br />\n<br />\nC# 既情況都係一樣, Advance Topic 既可以講 <br />\n- C++ 同 C# 之間點溝通<br />\n- C# GC 原理</blockquote><br />\nD人講到python好屈機咁"},{"pid":"34fed464cb5627793654f8eef7c29db2bc202ccb","tid":489564,"uid":76922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T02:38:31.000Z","msg":"巴艼有冇stack ,  recursion 同binary tree 啊？<br />\n留黎比我retake用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db8b19a241a24b314de0e028f2da3e10de62d059","tid":489564,"uid":76922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T02:40:31.000Z","msg":"其實想要c++多啲"},{"pid":"7cf11bcba7ce83aa5a11c352076e7f8caa7a6f65","tid":489564,"uid":70135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T02:44:44.000Z","msg":"樓主認為c++係未來兩三年會不會喺主流？"},{"pid":"250f15bcbcd369ffc551d52a2f7c7a8e7210b40d","tid":489564,"uid":49064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T02:57:07.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"8d92e3da2ba18db19461a00e149e1579fc3ff8e0","tid":489564,"uid":140573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T02:59:46.000Z","msg":"未睇先正評<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1ba3b2ae4dc5612a99916e117c5244fdbbb60eb","tid":489564,"uid":135971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T03:14:32.000Z","msg":"subscribed. assignment hell後煲一煲先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aebadd9c3e55974db8825b89fb09bfdf7000afc","tid":489564,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T03:25:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>會唔會講下cmake<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都可以既, 不過應該唔算太難, 如果明白 Makefile 係做咩<br />\n有無 D 有問題既實際例子, 咁我睇下用黎做示範<br />\n<br />\n另外因為我唔太喜歡 cmake, 所以自己整左個 Project Generator 出 VC, xcode, makefile<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://github.com/Jasonchan35/ax_project_gen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2FJasonchan35%2Fax_project_gen&d=ENFd%2Flb2Gs3BEX6GkT3qcDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=4cbaa15b\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/Jasonchan35/ax_project_gen</a></blockquote><br />\n你自己用就ok,但要release出去cmake應該無得避</blockquote><br />\n實際例子應該可以試下VTK + OpenCV 做3D rendering, 又或者opencv + qt 做GUI develop</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁都係既, <br />\n有無D用 cmake 時遇到困難既實際例子 ? 咁我可以準備下有咩要講</blockquote><br />\ncmake 最難係唔同library要對返岩version先compile到成條toolchain<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34d8cd062c9f8d0b39f27be6fb9cddd698b80298","tid":489564,"uid":35587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T03:27:05.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"57dc480207c7695f968343eaae952379b02084f0","tid":489564,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T03:27:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>會唔會講下python同c#</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果多人想要既話可以考慮下既, <br />\n<br />\n原本諗著唔係咁多人係學 Python / C# 入門時有大問題, 所以無諗著講<br />\n<br />\n反而 Python 做 Maya Plugin 就真係冷門 D, 可能唔知邊度學, 可以講下<br />\n<br />\nC# 既情況都係一樣, Advance Topic 既可以講 <br />\n- C++ 同 C# 之間點溝通<br />\n- C# GC 原理</blockquote><br />\nD人講到python好屈機咁</blockquote><br />\npython 起手快呀,一個pip install加個anaconda加個sublime text/ notepad++已經可以開波<br />\n<br />\n畫圖又有個抄matlab的matplotlib<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好多要efficiency既package底層又係c++寫加python interface"},{"pid":"e31654db0c0f424370bd914809fdde629b757056","tid":489564,"uid":10084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T03:42:17.000Z","msg":"見到巴打咁有心留個言先，遲下自學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"094837846085618c454a30d6fb0c30332e30547b","tid":489564,"uid":141110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T03:50:34.000Z","msg":"留名 準備sembreak學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d4419f7d5384af827e845756a3bdbf17684c06c","tid":489564,"uid":144849,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T05:52:00.000Z","msg":"多謝哂先 過2日考c++<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0967b217977acef4671995722329ddda5e2362e1","tid":489564,"uid":128613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T05:56:20.000Z","msg":"有冇c# 簡短教學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7548543a881aeb6fca954eb8e3599e43f445cde3","tid":489564,"uid":128613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T05:57:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇c# 簡短教學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想學黎寫unity game <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f2e22b9b2e3f302dc77d6d5713f44e440834f67","tid":489564,"uid":90890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T05:58:02.000Z","msg":"唔想學，但留名<br />\n（其實係想問下學完python再去學c會唔會有幫助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）"},{"pid":"e964d8c15dad9a40ad0808f577f4b9d3ecd92ef1","tid":489564,"uid":3,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T05:59:11.000Z","msg":"留名學野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d4348d06d4efd70185f7ae2f6153bef29a80302","tid":489564,"uid":5056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T06:51:33.000Z","msg":"想問下樓主點解可以學到咁深入<br />\n係工作緣故? 定純粹為興趣自學? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72711ff3417e2a2a13e1028b7c81ef67214ebd02","tid":489564,"uid":44908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T07:29:35.000Z","msg":"受教不少、比一般短片教學有提及更多歷史野 、可以更容易理解點解而家要咁做。"},{"pid":"1a6687f41bf64f0dda5f36f5aa66f7cb029c4b09","tid":489564,"uid":41509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T07:43:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主認為c++係未來兩三年會不會喺主流？</blockquote><br />\n由我學programming 開始，都未見過c++ 被非出主流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7030b48059e5d91e1df743f121c7cff9b19e94a","tid":489564,"uid":41509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T07:44:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主認為c++係未來兩三年會不會喺主流？</blockquote><br />\n由我學programming 開始，都未見過c++ 被飛出主流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"f744a08e80d7ce91ad4500e16e229ffb09ae5145","tid":489564,"uid":51592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T07:45:27.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"c5c4c911b9d6f297f6d8067f06ed70a94ebf1409","tid":489564,"uid":61505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T08:39:14.000Z","msg":"留名支持"},{"pid":"31f317fcebc5d587e08f1b3e8be11ffd0005f1fa","tid":489564,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T08:44:06.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"68cb1e6d1f45ea852eb40fda90055d208c714bf0","tid":489564,"uid":70135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T10:44:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓主認為c++係未來兩三年會不會喺主流？</blockquote><br />\n由我學programming 開始，都未見過c++ 被飛出主流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得c++雖然萬能<br />\n但近年多左好多新language <br />\nPython swift c#<br />\n用上手更方便<br />\n<br />\n講緊未來dL 為主<br />\n過程複雜過舊有program <br />\nC++出錯機會大過其他language 好多<br />\n<br />\n打個比喻<br />\n無理由有車仲要騎馬"},{"pid":"fa43222213e013fda3f5854a429687cde1add250","tid":489564,"uid":48679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T11:04:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓主認為c++係未來兩三年會不會喺主流？</blockquote><br />\n由我學programming 開始，都未見過c++ 被飛出主流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得c++雖然萬能<br />\n但近年多左好多新language <br />\nPython swift c#<br />\n用上手更方便<br />\n<br />\n講緊未來dL 為主<br />\n過程複雜過舊有program <br />\nC++出錯機會大過其他language 好多<br />\n<br />\n打個比喻<br />\n無理由有車仲要騎馬</blockquote><br />\n個比喻錯晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你話有原子筆點解要用毛筆就差唔多<br />\n新language 係方便，但performance 永遠比唔上c++"},{"pid":"45104784961b7a03bbf8adf1722c1999fc4fe966","tid":489564,"uid":131100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T11:14:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>會唔會講下python同c#</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果多人想要既話可以考慮下既, <br />\n<br />\n原本諗著唔係咁多人係學 Python / C# 入門時有大問題, 所以無諗著講<br />\n<br />\n反而 Python 做 Maya Plugin 就真係冷門 D, 可能唔知邊度學, 可以講下<br />\n<br />\nC# 既情況都係一樣, Advance Topic 既可以講 <br />\n- C++ 同 C# 之間點溝通<br />\n- C# GC 原理</blockquote><br />\nD人講到python好屈機咁</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好多做好既 Library 用咁囉, 用係方便既, 亦都唔係咩大小事都用 C++ 既<br />\n做 project 時都係睇須要決定用咩 Language<br />\nC++, C#, Python, Javascript, TypeScript, Lua 我平日都會用到"},{"pid":"75a50c7376eabc1125ca9aa7a8e8630f369d7f5d","tid":489564,"uid":131100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T11:17:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴艼有冇stack ,  recursion 同binary tree 啊？<br />\n留黎比我retake用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nStack 有講到呀, <br />\nRecursion 其實無咩特別, 就係 call 返自己囉, 只係睇著唔好爆 Stack<br />\n<br />\nB-Tree 既話, 都係 Pointer 好就無咩問題,<br />\n可以試下跟個 Doubly Linked List 個 Video<br />\n如果唔駛睇, 可以自己寫得返出黎既話, B-Tree 應該可以 handle 到<br />\n<br />\n再唔係就做下 A-star 做練習"},{"pid":"ba57b5fec16243e6894983762c214aa6a92f5c17","tid":489564,"uid":131100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T11:17:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實想要c++多啲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可以睇返 C++ 系列 Video"},{"pid":"019badf4dab75a5f25bd2d4c6d34588195398f09","tid":489564,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T11:18:09.000Z","msg":"support"},{"pid":"5e8ef581a834437ea994a853c251b7b1a4ad4575","tid":489564,"uid":131100,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T11:19:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>會唔會講下cmake<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都可以既, 不過應該唔算太難, 如果明白 Makefile 係做咩<br />\n有無 D 有問題既實際例子, 咁我睇下用黎做示範<br />\n<br />\n另外因為我唔太喜歡 cmake, 所以自己整左個 Project Generator 出 VC, xcode, makefile<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://github.com/Jasonchan35/ax_project_gen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2FJasonchan35%2Fax_project_gen&d=ENFd%2Flb2Gs3BEX6GkT3qcDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=4cbaa15b\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/Jasonchan35/ax_project_gen</a></blockquote><br />\n你自己用就ok,但要release出去cmake應該無得避</blockquote><br />\n實際例子應該可以試下VTK + OpenCV 做3D rendering, 又或者opencv + qt 做GUI develop</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁都係既, <br />\n有無D用 cmake 時遇到困難既實際例子 ? 咁我可以準備下有咩要講</blockquote><br />\ncmake 最難係唔同library要對返岩version先compile到成條toolchain<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係囉, 依個都唔知算唔算 cmake 既問題,<br />\n就算識用 cmake, 用到一D 3rd party lib, 都係要D 時間攪 compile<br />\n依個係大家做法唔統一既問題<br />\n<br />\n到最後就係要識睇晒 cmake, Makefile, gcc, 既 error message 先攪得掂"},{"pid":"415f6f261d168cf4360b8005db6bc66bb57a4260","tid":489564,"uid":131100,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T11:25:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇c# 簡短教學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想學黎寫unity game <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n考慮緊拍唔拍 C#,<br />\n雖然未必啱聽, 但係我真心建議學左 C -&gt; C++ 先學 C#<br />\n聽落可能好似要行遠左路, 但係學 C 既好處係會理解電腦運作<br />\n用 C# 未必睇得到底層做緊咩<br />\n<br />\n如果只係識 C# 唔識 C, 我見好多人(唔係全部) 都寫唔好 C#<br />\n而且好多時唔肯由 C/C++ 從頭學過, 但又進步唔到<br />\n<br />\n如果學 C 先, 可能都只係花多一兩個月時間, 但係畢生受用, 就算之後唔寫 C/C++"},{"pid":"4b3641a60e3f9a8d7528c79a6780ac206d006bb5","tid":489564,"uid":131100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T11:26:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔想學，但留名<br />\n（其實係想問下學完python再去學c會唔會有幫助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都會有既, 起碼 if, loop, function 之類已經識<br />\n但去到 pointer 後會見到分別"},{"pid":"fee6a16b302270e5e6c54274c52ee67c2b3c80dd","tid":489564,"uid":131100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T11:32:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問下樓主點解可以學到咁深入<br />\n係工作緣故? 定純粹為興趣自學? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n頭三四年係興趣自學, 之後就點死都搵份 C++ 既工, 就算係人工低都照做<br />\n之後係做過唔同公司唔同國家, 好多唔同類型既 Project, 一樣一樣慢慢磨返黎<br />\n就係咁磨左差唔多二十年<br />\n<br />\n依家拍左既 100 條 videos 大概係我 7 ~ 8 年所學既野, 所以已經係速成班"},{"pid":"866d98080fba262c7b0e0dd5671ddb1b05be7ea1","tid":489564,"uid":131100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T11:38:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓主認為c++係未來兩三年會不會喺主流？</blockquote><br />\n由我學programming 開始，都未見過c++ 被飛出主流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得c++雖然萬能<br />\n但近年多左好多新language <br />\nPython swift c#<br />\n用上手更方便<br />\n<br />\n講緊未來dL 為主<br />\n過程複雜過舊有program <br />\nC++出錯機會大過其他language 好多<br />\n<br />\n打個比喻<br />\n無理由有車仲要騎馬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n學 C/C++ 同用唔用係兩回事, 做 High Level 野用 Python, Swift, C# 都好正常<br />\n但係唔代表可以唔識個原理係點, 學 C++ 之所以用時間, 並唔係 C++ Syntax, Feature 本身, 反而用得最多時間係學 CPU, Memory, GPU, OS 點運作<br />\n<br />\n之於個比喻, 應該係, 就算馬車轉做汽車, 你都係要識同樣既物理原理"},{"pid":"87c1052993cb1798078892da9b657d7c01290a09","tid":489564,"uid":70135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T11:45:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓主認為c++係未來兩三年會不會喺主流？</blockquote><br />\n由我學programming 開始，都未見過c++ 被飛出主流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得c++雖然萬能<br />\n但近年多左好多新language <br />\nPython swift c#<br />\n用上手更方便<br />\n<br />\n講緊未來dL 為主<br />\n過程複雜過舊有program <br />\nC++出錯機會大過其他language 好多<br />\n<br />\n打個比喻<br />\n無理由有車仲要騎馬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n學 C/C++ 同用唔用係兩回事, 做 High Level 野用 Python, Swift, C# 都好正常<br />\n但係唔代表可以唔識個原理係點, 學 C++ 之所以用時間, 並唔係 C++ Syntax, Feature 本身, 反而用得最多時間係學 CPU, Memory, GPU, OS 點運作<br />\n<br />\n之於個比喻, 應該係, 就算馬車轉做汽車, 你都係要識同樣既物理原理</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但學完c++嘅唔好處喺<br />\n當你日常生活用電腦<br />\n你就會知好多人喺it界呃飯食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f9ba4471cf1579d82d93cfe80ba2d7ec2a007b7","tid":489564,"uid":131100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T11:48:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓主認為c++係未來兩三年會不會喺主流？</blockquote><br />\n由我學programming 開始，都未見過c++ 被飛出主流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得c++雖然萬能<br />\n但近年多左好多新language <br />\nPython swift c#<br />\n用上手更方便<br />\n<br />\n講緊未來dL 為主<br />\n過程複雜過舊有program <br />\nC++出錯機會大過其他language 好多<br />\n<br />\n打個比喻<br />\n無理由有車仲要騎馬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n學 C/C++ 同用唔用係兩回事, 做 High Level 野用 Python, Swift, C# 都好正常<br />\n但係唔代表可以唔識個原理係點, 學 C++ 之所以用時間, 並唔係 C++ Syntax, Feature 本身, 反而用得最多時間係學 CPU, Memory, GPU, OS 點運作<br />\n<br />\n之於個比喻, 應該係, 就算馬車轉做汽車, 你都係要識同樣既物理原理</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但學完c++嘅唔好處喺<br />\n當你日常生活用電腦<br />\n你就會知好多人喺it界呃飯食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁你要學埋隻眼開隻眼閉先得啦"},{"pid":"b0b36f2a671c9beaf12b24e8e6661aecff94a020","tid":489564,"uid":72667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T11:52:13.000Z","msg":"sub左樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己用開python，c++都係返學個時學得過1個學期，不過都係佢另我鍾意左programming<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"356b78b573b64d45a15dec26da85a124e2c96a78","tid":489564,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T12:27:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓主認為c++係未來兩三年會不會喺主流？</blockquote><br />\n由我學programming 開始，都未見過c++ 被飛出主流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得c++雖然萬能<br />\n但近年多左好多新language <br />\nPython swift c#<br />\n用上手更方便<br />\n<br />\n講緊未來dL 為主<br />\n過程複雜過舊有program <br />\nC++出錯機會大過其他language 好多<br />\n<br />\n打個比喻<br />\n無理由有車仲要騎馬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n學 C/C++ 同用唔用係兩回事, 做 High Level 野用 Python, Swift, C# 都好正常<br />\n但係唔代表可以唔識個原理係點, 學 C++ 之所以用時間, 並唔係 C++ Syntax, Feature 本身, 反而用得最多時間係學 CPU, Memory, GPU, OS 點運作<br />\n<br />\n之於個比喻, 應該係, 就算馬車轉做汽車, 你都係要識同樣既物理原理</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但學完c++嘅唔好處喺<br />\n當你日常生活用電腦<br />\n你就會知好多人喺it界呃飯食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nc++ 同 c嘅世界何等浩瀚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最近玩PCL真係睇doc都睇到嘔血<br />\n<br />\n之前仲寫c++ python embedding/c++ DL，仍然係覺得自己乜都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"656cbf7fd1712f36b114aa7ddeb92a7fce26ecdc","tid":489564,"uid":135928,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T14:27:30.000Z","msg":"巴打有冇教pointer同data file 自學撚唔係好識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e353083827fb5c0306f1175c6e1c77c41c8460e1","tid":489564,"uid":135928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T14:28:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打有冇教pointer同data file 自學撚唔係好識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nC"},{"pid":"a2209f3b0db152e1bf6e738c75dd946d49699a10","tid":489564,"uid":131100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T14:35:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打有冇教pointer同data file 自學撚唔係好識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有呀, 由咩都唔識開始學都得<br />\n<br />\nC 語言入門<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLeGk08zVu454WgM_8uE-dUayT_EOoVEQS\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fplaylist%3Flist%3DPLeGk08zVu454WgM_8uE-dUayT_EOoVEQS&d=ENFd%2Flb2Gs3BEX6GkT3qcDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=ca631c7a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLeGk08zVu454WgM_8uE-dUayT_EOoVEQS</a><br />\n<br />\n仲有 C 語言進階 同 C to C++, Advance C++"},{"pid":"923243350f8aea23a3ed89f4129cf67916f0f91f","tid":489564,"uid":126971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T19:08:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打好波"},{"pid":"782b6d9a5df42836916e46bbba978db44167fa09","tid":489564,"uid":131100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T19:37:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓主認為c++係未來兩三年會不會喺主流？</blockquote><br />\n由我學programming 開始，都未見過c++ 被飛出主流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得c++雖然萬能<br />\n但近年多左好多新language <br />\nPython swift c#<br />\n用上手更方便<br />\n<br />\n講緊未來dL 為主<br />\n過程複雜過舊有program <br />\nC++出錯機會大過其他language 好多<br />\n<br />\n打個比喻<br />\n無理由有車仲要騎馬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n學 C/C++ 同用唔用係兩回事, 做 High Level 野用 Python, Swift, C# 都好正常<br />\n但係唔代表可以唔識個原理係點, 學 C++ 之所以用時間, 並唔係 C++ Syntax, Feature 本身, 反而用得最多時間係學 CPU, Memory, GPU, OS 點運作<br />\n<br />\n之於個比喻, 應該係, 就算馬車轉做汽車, 你都係要識同樣既物理原理</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但學完c++嘅唔好處喺<br />\n當你日常生活用電腦<br />\n你就會知好多人喺it界呃飯食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nc++ 同 c嘅世界何等浩瀚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最近玩PCL真係睇doc都睇到嘔血<br />\n<br />\n之前仲寫c++ python embedding/c++ DL，仍然係覺得自己乜都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nPCL 無乜玩過喎, 有無 reference share 黎睇睇"},{"pid":"a9bd001f0322b65ba40e683f278191554cbc12aa","tid":489564,"uid":11802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T02:25:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"229b12cf95d5d92423bdb5fe74b074a777cfffdc","tid":489564,"uid":24592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T03:12:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4516b4c351a7f0692437d13a910d887c93d27a7","tid":489564,"uid":90890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T20:08:53.000Z","msg":"推，真心鐘意programming <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e587e0740ccfe4fefaf42f52c5c135bff4b0782a","tid":489564,"uid":116390,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T20:28:44.000Z","msg":"正呀，就考又好多野唔清<br />\n仲要廣東話<br />\n一次過煲晒黎急救<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a30d9d99e6334ffc6efc444722399a94e0a1075b","tid":489564,"uid":162508,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T05:31:18.000Z","msg":"謝謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n聖誕流流長 慢慢睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e96a83c8d9cb5bbc5fe83031